{"tid":642513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時開始，晶片變咗做芯片？","createTime":"2018-04-25T23:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T13:58:06.000Z","uid":144113,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ab086831c8db6cf6acb95a94a4a0d9d06e30e7ad","tid":642513,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8604cbc3ff742201d0d3c9a3a3702d8e181edf","tid":642513,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:08:01.000Z","msg":"問tvb"},{"pid":"921c7bca9f307e9822cd93e0b4a660e8f7907638","tid":642513,"uid":29804,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:26:14.000Z","msg":"中文詞彙地區差異比較&mdash;&mdash;#8「芯片」與「晶片」<br />\n<br />\n2011年12月31日&nbsp;作者:&nbsp;BYVoid&nbsp;正體版&nbsp;簡體版&nbsp;English<br />\n<br />\n#8（左邊爲大陸用詞，右邊爲臺灣用詞） 芯片 晶片<br />\n<br />\n「芯片」或「晶片」的英文是「chip」，其意義爲集成電路的載體。從其本意來講，「chip」是由「晶圓（wafer）」分割而成的小片，用於搭載集成電路，故「晶片」是較爲準確的翻譯。而「芯」本意爲一種草，引申義爲「燈芯」，現在也用於比喻「核心」。用在「芯片」一詞上，更多的是體現其「核心」的比喻義。因爲在一個電子系統中，芯片中的集成電路往往承載了整個系統最核心的功能，因此用「芯」來比喻也就可以理解了。<br />\n<br />\n我認爲從「信」、「達」角度來考慮，「晶片」之譯較爲優良，而自「雅」而觀之，則「芯片」更勝一籌。<br />\n<br />\n中国：芯片<br />\n香港：晶片"},{"pid":"6c6bdc4bcd2e5e7b6c8dc835ea57df05a2a98898","tid":642513,"uid":48234,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:28:56.000Z","msg":"支那蝗蟲話又入侵香港<br />\n睇吓硬件台就知蝗化得幾嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f21a2cd3550c4c5310aace0efe070c92570ef4f","tid":642513,"uid":99205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:46:09.000Z","msg":"文化入侵既後果<br />\n大陸人用龍芯做名<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人用英文 dragonball 或 model名"},{"pid":"985751fd77e8bf3aa059ed65447ab339efbaa058","tid":642513,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3f241b62580bc34e4b8e6759920d98aa9d02bd","tid":642513,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15368fe1a9e2e0b06d3597ac8688c44460e5ca16","tid":642513,"uid":152934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"屎晶片"},{"pid":"0714cd9633d8fb45780d4eaa7ecc2c245f3d9c37","tid":642513,"uid":30743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:49:41.000Z","msg":"參片<br />\n<br />\n花旗蔘？"},{"pid":"cfad2fe68069c7721352fcfa9a9ecd831341e568","tid":642513,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:52:31.000Z","msg":"不嬲叫cpu<br />\n單核雙核3核4核"},{"pid":"9dbea57d134c540082967cd01bd3b0e3d9fbb3d2","tid":642513,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffcb183d751e26ab49e198fa73219804a6157fd","tid":642513,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"你睇錯左大陸台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉返個正常頻道先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e304dbc6f45f4b4a6fc2073eb76c18386b7e21","tid":642513,"uid":9387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cfad2fe68069c7721352fcfa9a9ecd831341e568","tid":642513,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:52:31.000Z","msg":"不嬲叫cpu<br />\n單核雙核3核4核"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:57:43.000Z","msg":"Chip=Central processing unit?"},{"pid":"3a7c4a133dfbd637a16a132cd9bc6202e8d0b6a3","tid":642513,"uid":59695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"從來唔用「芯片」，語意